02T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Degree仔督察就ok<br />\n散仔就算啦同看更一樣咁頹，又無得點升</blockquote><br />\n好仔唔當差，當差正仆街<br />\n喺私人市場打左陣工，我已經覺寧願做一個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164a4456d1a8da6bd0ae67d258a118e85e12856b","tid":265831,"uid":72557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"督察級一定係慈母 人工高又威豬"},{"pid":"27f96fd14a83951f3f87480c266b94f50346e22b","tid":265831,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入境處先係最爽<br />\n高級看更</blockquote><br />\n上次等巴士見到拉左一堆蝻<br />\n好似幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw, 我中學fd做左五年懲教就變左懵柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d70b1a74193564d151a61e7778a745a7bcfa63","tid":265831,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入境處先係最爽<br />\n高級看更</blockquote><br />\n做到入境 青PASSPORT印 護照申請個啲位真係無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係你係有花，一係你申請政府文員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717fcbe08e7b39eb0caccb5306b8e45b9845f6c8","tid":265831,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海關真係咁好做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講升職前途<br />\n只講工作內容<br />\n可以講係一等一好做既紀律部隊<br />\n就算有骨頭位，都比其他好"},{"pid":"4586e012fd31a1819d8d54b238436984aaf988b1","tid":265831,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係入境啦 三年acting sia 七至十年坐正<br />\n海關冇廿碌都唔洗諗兩柴<br />\n不過工作性質上應該海關贏少少 海關隨機抽查 入境個個都要查晒證件</blockquote><br />\n唔知就咪9up啦<br />\n首先海關無兩柴得3柴<br />\n其次15年內升其實係正常水平<br />\n最fit既10年都升到（當然都無老移咁快）<br />\n但工作內容應該舒適好多"},{"pid":"8585552fc15f3e18214af67fcdf3127dcb563912","tid":265831,"uid":8631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梗係入境啦 三年acting sia 七至十年坐正<br />\n海關冇廿碌都唔洗諗兩柴<br />\n不過工作性質上應該海關贏少少 海關隨機抽查 入境個個都要查晒證件</blockquote><br />\n唔知就咪9up啦<br />\n首先海關無兩柴得3柴<br />\n其次15年內升其實係正常水平<br />\n最fit既10年都升到（當然都無老移咁快）<br />\n但工作內容應該舒適好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有朋友做緊海關 話唔行差踏錯都十五年後先開始考慮升"},{"pid":"621ec34b97b9b11ef87614d0092f55c60095640b","tid":265831,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T20:19:07.000Z","msg":"一講起海關掃毒<br />\n<br />\n諗起比門徒用鎚仔監生扑斷隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fb01f0494b717341f973c6ab9997ae66a84705","tid":265831,"uid":57980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T21:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梗係入境啦 三年acting sia 七至十年坐正<br />\n海關冇廿碌都唔洗諗兩柴<br />\n不過工作性質上應該海關贏少少 海關隨機抽查 入境個個都要查晒證件</blockquote><br />\n唔知就咪9up啦<br />\n首先海關無兩柴得3柴<br />\n其次15年內升其實係正常水平<br />\n最fit既10年都升到（當然都無老移咁快）<br />\n但工作內容應該舒適好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得之後好難再有十年十五年，只會愈嚟愈耐，係00年到04年嘅問題，少咗好多人同班9字爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw好似老移鑊氣無咁重"},{"pid":"8b492f788ce5247d4e45b80f8f64175d839ba490","tid":265831,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:10:05.000Z","msg":"冇人覺得做消防好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5b7781a10df55d38093098ed680c91f64256d0","tid":265831,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T23:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人覺得做消防好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n型但賣命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b127e76a859fb7b1d86648ee5d1b1ec9c7a37ed","tid":265831,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0